* * The dateElementOrder is based on the order of the * format specifiers in the formatPatterns.DatePattern. * * Example: 
   shortDatePattern    dateElementOrder
   ------------------  ----------------
   "M/d/yyyy"          "mdy"
   "dd/MM/yyyy"        "dmy"
   "yyyy-MM-dd"        "ymd"
* * The correct dateElementOrder is required by the parser to * determine the expected order of the date elements in the * string being parsed.

   * within the parser.

   * to the Datejs Forum located at http://www.datejs.com/forums/.
